      "role": "user",
      "content": "exactly. \"creating your own meaning\" just feels like a coping mechanism, right? like telling yourself a story so you don't scream at the void. it's just a way to stay busy while the clock ticks down to nothing. if the end result is always zero, why do we have to endure all the pain and the mess of being alive along the way? it feels so irrational to keep pushing through it.",
